## DidResolverCacheNoop variable

no-op cache that is used as the default cache for did-resolver. The motivation behind using a no-op cache as the default stems from the desire to maximize the potential for this library to be used in as many JS runtimes as possible

**Signature:**

```typescript
DidResolverCacheNoop: DidResolverCache
```
